==Diane Tchuindjo 

~~~
{}{img_left}{Diane_Tchuindjo.jpg}{}{325}{375}{}
 

I am a first year graduate student in the [https://datascience.ucsd.edu/ Data Science Department] at the University of California, San Diego. My research interests lie broadly in probability theory, statistics, and optimization.

Previously, I completed my undergraduate degree in mathematics and economics at the University of Maryland, College Park. During my time as an undergraduate student I interned at [https://www.msri.org/ MSRI], the Department of Defense, and [https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/research-area/quantum-computing/? Microsoft Quantum]. After graduating, I spent some time as a research engineer and mathematician at ["https://apogee-research.com/ Apogee Research] and [https://envieta.com/ Envieta] respectively.

*Incoming News:* I am currently spending part of my time at [https://redpoll.ai/ Redpoll AI] working on probabilistic ML!


